error.message: Parameter $tempStoreFactory of method Drupal\sms_vbo\Form\SmsVboConfirmAction::__construct() has typehint with deprecated class Drupal\user\PrivateTempStoreFactory. Deprecated in drupal:8.5.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\TempStore\PrivateTempStoreFactory instead.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to sms_vbo.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
